OL,3,CConsultants in England agree new pay
OL,4,Coffer from government
OL,6,FConsultants have accepted a pay offer,
OL,7,Fending a year-long dispute with the
OL,8,Fgovernment, the British Medical
OL,9,FAssociation (BMA) has announced.
OL,11,FAn overwhelming, 83% (62% turnout) of
OL,12,Feligible consultant members voted in
OL,13,Ffavour of the offer and the BMA's
OL,14,Fconsultants committee has now formally
OL,15,Faccepted it, according to the union.
OL,17,FMembers of the Hospital Consultants
OL,18,Fand Specialists Association (HCSA)
OL,19,Falso voted - by 83% - to accept the
OL,20,Foffer.
