OL,3,CConsultants in England agree new pay
OL,4,Coffer from government
OL,6,FThe deal includes a 2.85% (#3,000)
OL,7,Fuplift for those who have been
OL,8,Fconsultants between four and seven
OL,9,Fyears, who under the original offer
OL,10,Freceived no additional uplift, said
OL,11,Fthe BMA.
OL,13,FThe offer is in addition to the 6%
OL,14,Fawarded during the DDRB process last
OL,15,Fsummer.
OL,17,FTheir vote brings an end to ongoing
OL,18,Fstrike action, adding to the NHS
OL,19,Fpatient appointment waiting list,
OL,20,Fwhich has also been affected by the
OL,21,Funresolved junior doctors' dispute.
