OL,3,CConsultants in England agree new pay
OL,4,Coffer from government
OL,6,FThe consultants are to receive their
OL,7,Fpay increases in coming months, which
OL,8,Fwill be backdated to March, the BMA
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThis boost will help reduce gender pay
OL,12,Fgap in medicine, by delivering a key
OL,13,Frecommendation made by Professor Dame
OL,14,FJane Dacre in her review on the gender
OL,15,Fpay gap in medicine.
OL,17,FConsultants will also be offered
OL,18,Fenhanced shared parental leave.
