OL,3,CConsultants in England agree new pay
OL,4,Coffer from government
OL,6,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak said: "The
OL,7,Fend of consultant strike action in the
OL,8,FNHS is excellent news for patients.
OL,10,F"It will mean we can continue making
OL,11,Fprogress towards our goal of cutting
OL,12,Fthe waiting lists, which have now
OL,13,Ffallen for the fourth month in a row.
OL,15,F"Consultants perform a vital role at
OL,16,Fthe heart of the NHS ` I'm pleased
OL,17,Fthey've accepted this deal, which is
OL,18,Ffair for them and fair for the
OL,19,Ftaxpayer."
