OL,3,CConsultants in England agree new pay
OL,4,Coffer from government
OL,6,FHealth and Social Care Secretary
OL,7,FVictoria Atkins said: "I hugely value
OL,8,Fthe work of NHS consultants and I am
OL,9,Fpleased that, after weeks of
OL,10,Fnegotiations, they have accepted this
OL,11,Ffair and reasonable offer, putting an
OL,12,Fend to the threat of further strike
OL,13,Faction.
OL,15,F"This deal directly addresses gender
OL,16,Fpay issues in the NHS and enhances
OL,17,Fconsultants' parental leave options `
OL,18,Frepresenting a fair deal for
OL,19,Fconsultants, patients, and taxpayers."
