OL,3,CConsultants in England agree new pay
OL,4,Coffer from government
OL,6,FConsultants' core contract has not
OL,7,Fbeen updated for 20 years and this
OL,8,Foffer will deliver reform to reflect
OL,9,Fmodern ways of working, such as
OL,10,Fenhanced shared parental leave, in
OL,11,Fline with other NHS staff.
OL,13,FThe BMA said the deal has also made
OL,14,Fimportant changes to the profession's
OL,15,Fpay review body (DDRB), which
OL,16,Frepresents "significant progress" in
OL,17,Freturning it to its "original purpose
OL,18,Fand independence".
