OL,3,CConsultants in England agree new pay
OL,4,Coffer from government
OL,6,F"These changes mean that the DDRB can
OL,7,Fno longer ignore the historical losses
OL,8,Fthat doctors have suffered or the fact
OL,9,Fthat countries abroad are competing
OL,10,Ffor UK doctors with the offer of
OL,11,Fsignificantly higher salaries, a BMA
OL,12,Fspokesperson said.
OL,14,F"The offer also improves on the
OL,15,Fprevious proposal to reform the
OL,16,Fconsultant pay scale."
OL,18,FTalks between the government and the
OL,19,Funions were reopened in February after
OL,20,Fthe initial offer was narrowly
OL,21,Frejected the previous month.
