OL,3,CConsultants in England agree new pay
OL,4,Coffer from government
OL,6,FThe deal continues to invest in
OL,7,Fmodernising the consultants' pay
OL,8,Fstructure ` reducing the number of pay
OL,9,Fpoints and the time it takes to reach
OL,10,Fthe top, effective from March 1.
OL,12,FThe BMA has also agreed to end the use
OL,13,Fof its rate card, which advises
OL,14,Fdoctors on how much to charge for non-
OL,15,Fcontractual work, including cover
OL,16,Fduring strikes.
